{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8106","title":"NG8106: Suffix not supported","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8106-suffix-not-supported\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"af9haos754j2juq9lxmbp39nd\">NG8106: Suffix not supported<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#ng8106-suffix-not-supported\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7dph0ohargsfo8391kwlonfpt\">此診斷會檢測 <code>.px</code> 、 <code>.%</code> 和 <code>.em</code> 字尾何時與屬性繫結一起使用。這些字尾僅適用於樣式繫結。</p>\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n\n&lt;div [attr.width.px]=\"5\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7bicb9bjjdedhs8bfd5vdiby7\">我該怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6nafvmbmee0iglt9hm8ffsxw\">與其使用只能在樣式繫結中受支援的 <code>.px</code> 、 <code>.%</code> 或 <code>.em</code> 字尾，不如將其移動到對繫結進行賦值的表示式中。</p>\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n  \n&lt;div [attr.width]=\"'5px'\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"duupn560xw3oqrkqmgen1ccwo\">如果我無法避免這種情況怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bzu6yb6isvsmddbdryz1qwy7l\">可以透過編輯專案的 <code>tsconfig.json</code> 檔案來停用此診斷：</p>\n<code-example format=\"json\" language=\"json\">\n\n{\n  \"angularCompilerOptions\": {\n    \"extendedDiagnostics\": {\n      \"checks\": {\n        \"suffixNotSupported\": \"suppress\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1tl6suaasu3xo2b1onvdft0o9\">有關更多訊息，請參閱<a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">擴充套件診斷設定</a>。</p>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics#configuration\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#ng8106-suffix-not-supported\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-if-i-cant-avoid-this\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8106#what-should-i-do-instead\n-->"}